{"tid":972513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8警圍捕都搞唔掂 野豬狂奔500米匿入學校","createTime":"2019-01-07T12:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T12:43:22.000Z","uid":184261,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62a34d42c1c6fd42c616f904b046069b82a5ca0b","tid":972513,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:13:06.000Z","msg":"筲箕灣野豬出沒注意！下午4時許，一隻身長約1米的野豬在東濤苑內閒蕩，多名居民見狀立即四散，人心惶惶，警方接報後立即派員到場，其間野豬懷疑受驚，走到旁邊的愛寶樓對開花槽，瑟縮一角。10多名警員到場增援，其中8名警員手持盾牌及警棍圍捕，並在附近垃圾站借來一個大型垃圾桶，打算將野豬困住，惟野豬不停掙扎，最後跳過垃圾桶逃走。野豬不停與警員大玩「心理戰」，你追我躲，其後更跑入500米外的筲箕灣崇真學校內，警方仍在現場嘗試捕捉野豬。"},{"pid":"4299165e61497ab5c0ee44a96f364bcb93f763ba","tid":972513,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"下午4時許，<br />\n警方仍在現場嘗試捕捉野豬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b564e33d8b99fae6cb6900326c8454038c9e36","tid":972513,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:15:12.000Z","msg":"諗起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CUcDDNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCUcDDNX.jpg&h=425ca139&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82f3c2e8bf016355ad3cc56d592d05478b39d5fb","tid":972513,"uid":123657,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"要捉支那豬唔係咁易ga"},{"pid":"6bf7d69a1237849be06fb6eb4c858aba904dbb0f","tid":972513,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:17:04.000Z","msg":"東濤苑? 點樣走到去嗰度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094172baed812ce7ef3161e42c2a4def379df382","tid":972513,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:21:37.000Z","msg":"動保撚批鬥咗筲箕灣街坊未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係啲街坊搬入嚟啲野豬咪可以通街跑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c002484c59d2c352e51eaeee7ff91e0145993cd","tid